name: Dystopian Hours III- Heartbreak
description: Teatro del Mondo is where the big battle with Heartbreak takes place. A temporary building on the water, the perfect spot for such a confrontation. You know it has no foundation and yet it tricks you into thinking it will be there forever. It’s probably the most difficult fear to face, mostly because you think you have no chance against it. It toys with your soul, leaving you desperate, small and completely helpless. But if you hold on to your heart long enough, one day it will finally be gone and the waters will be clear again. Did you ever have your heart broken?
